switchAction 
Game: ARMA 2  (1.00) 
Description: When used on a person, the given action is started immediately (there 
 is no transition). Use switchmove "" to switch back to the default 
 movement if there is no transition back, otherwise the person may be stuck 
.  
Syntax:  
 soldier switchAction action 
Parameters: 
soldier: Object 
action: String 
Return Value: 
 Nothing